title: Bug 25946[Dialogs] ElementTreeSelectionDialog.getFirstResult() should return null
OB: ElementTreeSelectionDialog.getFirstResult() returns the currently selectedelement if you cancel the Dialog using the window's X button (on the top righthand corner of the window).The return value should be null, just like what you get when the user pressesthe Cancel button.
